{"tid":1862118,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護之外，到清潔界了","createTime":"2020-02-04T12:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:54:54.000Z","uid":102840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"230c913b0c9dd8776aff041d8b10d4fe29559d2e","tid":1862118,"uid":102840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"她坦言，「以前公司(對口罩)好闊綽」，負責掃地及收拾垃圾等清潔工人，每個月至少可獲一盒50個裝的口罩，不足夠亦可再取。惟現在市面上「一罩難求」，有清潔公司甚至「去埋印尼、泰國同加拿大都買唔到」，只好採用登記制度，按工作需要發放口罩。<br />\n<br />\n面臨停工，甄認為只有政府有能力提供口罩應急，並去信特首林鄭月娥，要求她調撥500萬個口罩予業界應急。若港府明日(5日)仍未能作出回應，聯盟將考慮於周四(6日)召開記者會，向全港市民解釋業界即將停工的原因。她指出，業界期望港府盡力提供口罩，或優先提供予政府的外判清潔工人，「過得一日得一日啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200204/mobile/bkn-20200204173045425-0204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200204%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200204173045425-0204_00822_001.html&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=bf0a11f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200204/mobile/bkn-20200204173045425-0204_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n緊係買唔撚到啦，比林鄭截晒啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://jchann.net/view2/56482/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjchann.net%2Fview2%2F56482%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=bd8bda9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://jchann.net/view2/56482/</a>"},{"pid":"faa6e21c50026fbbc24b71fd878364f076168891","tid":1862118,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"究竟去晒邊？<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】陳肇始：新年假期後數批口罩運抵零售點<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2v6xCFu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v6xCFu&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=6090bd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2v6xCFu</a>"},{"pid":"d275ba05428fce5a093894f43beaa2bf5fb41be0","tid":1862118,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"做得